    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Radicalization Of James Woolsey</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>W D Howells letter on Andrew Cockburn's July 23 article supports James Woolsey's attempt to prevent deportation of Iraqi men to their homeland</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>This is the kind of thing that breathes reality into Oliver Stone's fantasies. Woolsey got it right when he called it Fascism.</p>
        <p>W.D. Howells  Washington</p>
      </block>
